{"tid":2013824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】星加坡單日新增884宗個案　累計破2萬4千宗","createTime":"2020-05-12T14:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T16:39:04.000Z","uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b824d1eff5d72061b011c5461bda2eb5b620eba","tid":2013824,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/%E6%98%9F%E5%B7%9E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%A0%B42%E8%90%AC3%E5%8D%83%E5%AE%97-1-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B7%259E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%25A0%25B42%25E8%2590%25AC3%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%25AE%2597-1-1024x576.jpg&h=ccadaf41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【癲狗日報報道】武漢肺炎疫情肆虐全球，星加坡疫情持續不斷，確診人數為香港的20多倍，今日（十二）再新增884宗確診個案，累計確診個案破2萬4千宗，續成東南亞之冠。<br />\n<br />\n星加坡衛生部今日通報，當地單日再新增884人確診，其中絕大多數患者仍然為外勞，僅3人是新加坡公民及永久居民，全國累計確診個案達2萬4671例宗。另外，昨日再新增1人死亡，全國累計21人不治。<br />\n<br />\n星加坡由於外勞宿舍爆發大規模群感組染，導致當地自4月初以來，確診人數連日爆增，每日確診人數至少維持3位數的增長，早前更一度連續4日單日破千宗。<br />\n<br />\n雖然當地確診人數仍然高居不下，但星加坡本地社區新增病例近來已呈現下降趨勢。當地政府決定自今日起放寬部分限制措施，部分商店，例如髮廊屋、餅店以及洗衣店可以重開，但要遵守嚴格的防疫措施，任何訪客和職員進出店舖時，都必須使用政府的官方應用程式簽到，登記個人資料，以便一但有人確診時可以方便追蹤其密切接觸者和到訪地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/05/12/newsdesk/international/星加坡單日新增884宗個案-累計破2萬4千宗/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2Fnewsdesk%2Finternational%2F%E6%98%9F%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E884%E5%AE%97%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E7%A0%B42%E8%90%AC4%E5%8D%83%E5%AE%97%2F&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=39907d04\" target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/05/12/newsdesk/international/星加坡單日新增884宗個案-累計破2萬4千宗/</a>"},{"pid":"c5ffb1659280edbe51f54b2e48b75357dffe01c8","tid":2013824,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/%E6%98%9F%E5%B7%9E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%A0%B42%E8%90%AC3%E5%8D%83%E5%AE%97-1-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B7%259E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%25A0%25B42%25E8%2590%25AC3%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%25AE%2597-1-1024x576.jpg&h=ccadaf41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad62846dada2d93d54c822f7b147dcf2a66f35f8","tid":2013824,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b80749585742f66dada4d6f4975050cf8696e7b","tid":2013824,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cd980d302b0149d46b9499d12abeabfb46e117","tid":2013824,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"Monkeypore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f6f65865228cba1a5c25413a9add356cba2aba","tid":2013824,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"o fucking yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji